rows.label: tlk45300012_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I can't get over the fact that you're
providing for your village at such a
young age, Rex. It's really admirable.

rows.label: tlk45300012_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You're probably heading
out for a bit of salvaging
after this, aren't you?

rows.label: tlk45300012_01_msg0003
rows.name: Well, be careful how you go.

rows.label: tlk45300012_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Come to me whenever you need to
send some cash back to Iyasaki.
